    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A deadly attack created by the Aburame as a way to quickly eliminate a single opponent by sending multiple swarms of symbiotes at the opponent where they attack in a swirling motion, much like a tornado. The opponent suffers 1d4 points of chakra damage per swarm, and must succeed a fortitude save or be nauseated for 1 round.<br><br>The cost is 8+2 chakra for each additional swarm, up to a max of 1 per 3 levels of the user.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Requires:</b> ; Kikai Host</p>\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> At first, third and fifth step mastery, gain +1 chakra damage per swarm.</p>\n",
